section.def:
advertise (宣傳)
            includes issuing a catalogue, circular or price list that is intended for the general
            public;

paragraph.content:
a book, voucher, receipt or data material, or information which is recorded
                    in a non-legible form but is capable of being reproduced in a legible form;
                    and

a chairman and a deputy chairman each of whom shall be a barrister
                    qualified to practise as such or a solicitor qualified to act as such under the
                    Legal Practitioners Ordinance (Cap. 159);

impose additional safety standards or requirements for toys, including more
                    stringent standards or requirements in relation to a matter provided for in any
                    one or more of the toy standards;
